channel.title: EyreScape709 Under Development
channel.description:
Welcome to EyreScape709! This is the new Dedicated server I (Humid) Has Made! This is a project I've been working on for many months.
Development team: Humid
Here is my Progress:
Green - Finished Yellow - In progress Red - Not Started
Combat: Finish all Spells Rewrite NPC Combat Rewrite ranging Rewrite PVP
Skills: Construction Dungeoneering Summoning with Charm Drops & Shard Drops Finish Up runecrafting Slayer Hunter Farming
Minigames: Pest Control Warriors guild Duel Arena Finish Dominion Tower Soul Wars Clan Wars Safe PVP / Unsafe pvp
Misc:
Fix memory leaks Fix GPI Fix sendItemsOnDeath Fix Random Server nulls Trading Fix The Pots In Pvm & Wild Fix Decompiled code
1 Pic:
[IMG]http://i43.tinypic.com/2ik9slf.png[/img]
Thanks All,
Owner & Coder,
Humid
